                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6486" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0621</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8219 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华宏“随风起舞”的底层逻辑：戴华的企业家精神</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Underlying Logic of Huahong&#39;s &quot;Dancing with the Wind&quot;: The entrepreneurial spirit of Dai Hua</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁亮，范子成，龚家英，郑诗文，谢文雄</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华宏汽车集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；机会识别与开发；机会窗口；华宏；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Entrepreneurship; Opportunity Identification and Development; Opportunity Window; Hua Hong.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业的成长离不开企业家对机会的识别和开发，在这个过程中，企业家精神是核心内驱力。华宏汽车集团有限公司是一家以“诚信经营，锤炼百年华宏”为目标，集汽车销售、汽车金融、精品、美容等汽车服务为一体的汽车经销企业。本案例以华宏集团的发展为主线，描述了自1994年创业以来，集团创始人戴华准确识别机会，把握机会带领企业发展壮大的过程，重点突出了创业过程中戴华创新创业、坚持诚信经营、践行社会责任的企业家精神。2020年疫情爆发之际，戴华更是将社会责任展现的淋漓尽致，第一时间捐款捐物，实施“停工不停薪”，与国家共同抗疫。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The growth of an enterprise is inseparable from the recognition and development of opportunities by entrepreneurs, in which entrepreneurship is the core internal driving force. Huahong Automobile Group is an automobile distribution enterprise with the goal of &quot;operating in good faith, building a century-old Huahong&quot;, and integrating automobile sales, automobile finance, fine products, beauty and other automobile services. Taking the development of Huahong Group as the main line, this case describes the process that Dai Hua, the founder of the group, has accurately identified opportunities and grasped them to lead the development and growth of the enterprise since it started its business in 1994, highlighting Dai Hua&#39;s entrepreneurial spirit of innovating and starting a business, adhering to honest management and practicing social responsibility. When the epidemic broke out in 2020, Dai Hua showed his social responsibility vividly, donating money and materials at the first time, implementing &quot;stopping work without pay&quot;, and fighting the epidemic together with the state. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《企业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机会窗口理论；机会识别与开发；创业警觉性；企业家精神</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
